==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Clary
<hw>Cla"ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. LL.
<ets>sclarea</ets>, <ets>scarlea</ets>, D. & G. <ets>scharlei</ets>, F.
<ets>sclar⟦eacute⟧e</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A plant
(<spn>Salvia sclarea</spn>) of the Sage family, used in flavoring
soups.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Clary water</b></col>, <cd>a composition of clary flowers
with brandy, etc., formerly used as a cardiac.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

